title: "Control-Systems Research Template"
abstract: >-
  A MATLAB/Spyder-style Python template for academic robot-control research,
  AI-collaboration ready (CLAUDE.md + AGENTS.md). Stack: Pinocchio for
  rigid-body dynamics, python-control, and custom Runge-Kutta integrators.
